弃水下泄，不该引的部分多余引水量在可引水量计算时暂未考虑。多余引水量可由石山口水库加入引水后调节的弃水量与未加入引水量时调节的弃水量之差求得，可引水量减去多余引水量为实际应引水量，成果见表4。</p><table-wrap id="table4" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table4">Table 4</xref></label><caption><title> The result of actual water diversio</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle" >年份</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >可引水量(万m<sup>3</sup>)</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >实引水量(万m<sup>3</sup>)</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >年份</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >可引水量(万m<sup>3</sup>)</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >实引水量(万m<sup>3</sup>)</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >年份</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >可引水量(万m<sup>3</sup>)</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >实引水量(万m<sup>3</sup>)</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >1976</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1489</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1489</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1989</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >5180</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2171</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2002</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >4838</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >4282</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >1977</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >3964</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >3964</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1990</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >4765</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1050</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2003</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >6909</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >3096</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >1978</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >796</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >796</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1991</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >6353</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >3011</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2004</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >4040</td><td align="center